& = & \frac{3(a+b+1)(2a^2 -2ab + 2b^2 + a^2b + ab^2)}{ab(a+b+2)(a+b+3)}-3 = \frac{6\bb{(a-b)^2 (a+b + 1) - ab (a+b+ 2)}}{ab (a+b + 2) (a+b + 3)}.
